text: An Adventuress is a 1920 American drama movie directed by Fred J. Balshofer and starring Rudolph Valentino, Julian Eltinge, Virginia Rappe, Leo White. It was distributed by Republic Distributing Corporation. ==Other websites== * * Category:1920 drama movies Category:1922 drama movies Category:American LGBT movies Category:American drama movies Category:American silent movies
